WEBVTT

00:11:27.953 --> 00:11:30.207
when there is so much information

00:11:30.207 --> 00:11:32.204
out there in the open,

00:11:32.204 --> 00:11:33.878
why should this crucial information

00:11:33.878 --> 00:11:35.388
about company ownership

00:11:35.388 --> 00:11:37.094
stay hidden away?

00:11:37.094 --> 00:11:40.819
Why should tax evaders, corrupt 
government officials,

00:11:40.819 --> 00:11:43.071
arms traders and more,

00:11:43.071 --> 00:11:47.109
be able to hide their identities from us, the public?

00:11:47.109 --> 00:11:52.738
Why should this secrecy be such 
an accepted business practice?

00:11:52.738 --> 00:11:54.426
Anonymous companies

00:11:54.426 --> 00:11:56.635
might be the norm right now

00:11:56.635 --> 00:11:58.641
but it wasn't always this way.

00:11:58.641 --> 00:12:00.438
Companies were created